"Cubed tofu fried in sesame oil and then soaked in soy sauce. Healthy and "
"delicious."
msgstr "豆腐塊用芝麻油炸過後浸泡在醬油中。健康又美味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "edamame"
msgid_plural "edamame"
msgstr[0] "毛豆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'edamame', 'str_pl': 'edamame'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Edamame, otherwise known as soy beans. With a little sauce and a beer these "
