msgstr "一種標誌性的糕點，內餡是濃郁美味的蛋奶凍，頂部覆蓋著黑巧克力糖霜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "garlic bread"
msgid_plural "garlic bread"
msgstr[0] "蒜香麵包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'garlic bread', 'str_pl': 'garlic bread'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A loaf of french bread with a slathering of garlic-infused butter on the "
"inside, in a convenient ready-to-bake foil-lined paper bag."
msgstr "一條法式麵包，內部塗滿了蒜香黃油，裝在方便即烤的錫紙襯裡紙袋中。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "garlic bread (cooked)"
msgid_plural "garlic bread (cooked)"
msgstr[0] "蒜香麵包（已烹飪）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'garlic bread (cooked)', 'str_pl': 'garlic bread
#. (cooked)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
