"A dainty pastry covered with a thin layer of custard that is in turn "
"overlaid with fruit syrup and fruit. This particular one is laden with "
"raspberries."
msgstr "一種精緻的糕點，覆蓋著一層薄薄的蛋奶凍，上面又覆蓋著水果糖漿和水果。這個特別的是滿載覆盆子。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tart'}
