msgstr "一個柔軟、新鮮出爐的卷狀糕點，內層鋪滿粘稠的肉桂紅糖，外層覆蓋著厚厚的奶油糖霜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "corn bread"
msgid_plural "corn breads"
msgstr[0] "玉米麵包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'corn bread'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A country classic. Moist, sweet, and squeezable."
msgstr "鄉村經典。溼潤、香甜，且易於擠壓。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "scone"
msgid_plural "scones"
msgstr[0] "司康餅"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'scone'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A scone filled with New England cranberry jam. Tart, yet delicious."
msgstr "一個夾有新英格蘭蔓越莓果醬的司康餅。酸澀，卻美味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'scone'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A scone filled with New England blueberry jam. Sweet and delightful."
msgstr "一個夾有新英格蘭藍莓果醬的司康餅。甜美而令人愉悅。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "bagel"
msgid_plural "bagels"
msgstr[0] "貝果"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bagel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A plain bagel."
msgstr "一個原味貝果。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bagel'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A supreme bagel with five kinds of seeds atop a light layer of toasted "
"cheddar cheese. Secretly good for you."
msgstr "一個至尊貝果，表面撒有五種種子，並覆蓋一層輕烤切達奶酪。暗地裡對你有益。"

#: .\comestibles.json
