msgstr "這是一打能多益夾心餅乾，新鮮出爐。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "baguette"
msgid_plural "baguettes"
msgstr[0] "法棍麵包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'baguette'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A warm french baguette with beautiful score lines. It's almost a tragedy to "
"eat this!"
msgstr "一條溫熱的法棍麵包，有著漂亮的割紋。吃掉它簡直是種罪過！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "muffins"
msgid_plural "muffins"
msgstr[0] "瑪芬蛋糕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A dozen poppyseed muffins. Moderately sweet with a subtle chewiness."
msgstr "一打罌粟籽瑪芬蛋糕。甜度適中，略帶嚼勁。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dozen blueberry muffins. Sweet, slightly dry, but with plenty of tanginess"
" from the fresh blueberries throughout."
msgstr "一打藍莓瑪芬蛋糕。香甜，略幹，但新鮮的藍莓遍佈其中，帶來濃郁的酸爽風味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dozen cinnamon coffee cake muffins. Deli-quality melted butter and brown "
"sugar veins throughout, with a generous crumb topping of cinnamon and brown "
"sugar. It doesn't get much better than this."
msgstr "一打肉桂咖啡蛋糕瑪芬。內部遍佈熟食店品質的融化黃油和紅糖紋路，頂部慷慨地撒滿了肉桂和紅糖碎屑。沒有比這更好的了。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dozen banana nut muffins. Exceptionally moist and smooth, these almost "
"melt in your mouth."
msgstr "一打香蕉堅果瑪芬蛋糕。異常溼潤順滑，幾乎入口即化。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dozen luscious chocolate muffins. Entirely infused with chocolate, right "
"down to thick chunks of chewy fudge and chocolate chunks throughout."
msgstr "一打濃郁巧克力瑪芬蛋糕。完全浸潤了巧克力，內部遍佈厚實的耐嚼軟糖塊和巧克力塊。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dozen oreo chocolate muffins. Studded with oreo cookie bits and drizzled "
"with melted oreo cream. The best kind of volcanic eruption."
msgstr "一打奧利奧巧克力瑪芬蛋糕。點綴著奧利奧餅乾碎，淋上了融化的奧利奧奶油。這是最美妙的火山噴發。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dozen pumpkin muffins. Moist and velvety, with just enough spice to bring "
"out the edge."
msgstr "一打南瓜瑪芬蛋糕。溼潤絲滑，香料恰到好處，凸顯了風味層次。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dozen pound cake muffins. Modestly sweet and buttery with a smooth glaze."
msgstr "一打磅蛋糕瑪芬。甜度適中，黃油味濃郁，表面有一層光滑的糖霜。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muffins', 'str_pl': 'muffins'}
#: .\comestibles.json
