" with thick layers of artificial flavoring."
msgstr "許多小朋友的冠軍早餐。重度加工，覆蓋著厚厚的人工調味層。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "survivor cookie"
msgid_plural "survivor cookies"
msgstr[0] "倖存者餅乾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor cookie'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Improvised cookies, often made with non-standard ingredients. Their flavor "
"varies wildly from cookie to cookie as a result. Good in a pinch, but not "
"nearly as good as a commercial mix. Due to being made mostly with dry "
"ingredients, these keep for a long time."
msgstr ""
"臨時製作的餅乾，通常使用非標準原料。因此，每塊餅乾的味道差異極大。緊急情況下不錯，但遠不如商業混合品。由於主要由幹原料製成，這些餅乾能保存很長時間。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "deli tray"
msgid_plural "deli trays"
msgstr[0] "熟食托盤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli tray'}
