msgid_plural "deli platters"
msgstr[0] "熟食拼盤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deli platter'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A round plastic deli platter with a tall fitted transparent plastic lid. "
"Normally used for larger displays like cheesecake and samplers."
msgstr "一個圓形塑料熟食拼盤，配有高大的合適透明塑料蓋。通常用於較大展示，如芝士蛋糕和樣品拼盤。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "rigid plastic case"
msgid_plural "rigid plastic cases"
msgstr[0] "硬質塑料箱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rigid plastic case'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A large, rigid plastic case normally used to store 30 day emergency food "
"supplies or cat litter."
msgstr "一個大型硬質塑料箱，通常用於儲存30天應急食品或貓砂。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "plastic tub"
msgid_plural "plastic tubs"
msgstr[0] "塑料桶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plastic tub'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A wide-mouthed plastic tub with a screw-on lid. Normally used for storing "
"dry powder."
msgstr "一個廣口塑料桶，配有旋蓋。通常用於儲存乾粉。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "large plastic cup"
msgid_plural "large plastic cups"
msgstr[0] "大塑料杯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large plastic cup'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A clear plastic cup with a wide mouth and fitted lid. Normally used for "
"holding individual deli soup and salad servings."
msgstr "一個透明塑料杯，廣口並配有合適的蓋子。通常用於盛裝單獨的熟食湯和沙拉份餐。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Gourmand's Graces"
msgstr "美食家的恩賜"

#. ~ Description for Gourmand's Graces
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Greatly expands the selection of various cooked food you can find in grocery"
" stores and pharmacy fridges. Focuses on items you'd expect to find in "
"bakery and deli departments."
msgstr "極大地擴展了你在雜貨店和藥店冰箱中可以找到的各種熟食選擇。專注於你期望在烘焙區和熟食區找到的物品。"

#. ~ Sign
#: .\teashop.json
msgid "The Red Dragon Tea Shop"
msgstr "紅龍茶館"
